dct_title_s: Java, Madura & Bali 1:250,000 / prepared under the direction of the Chief of Engineers, U.S. Army, by the Army Map Service.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Contour interval 100 meters." First ed. gives heights in feet with contour interval of 250 or 500 feet. Shows 5 classes of roads or trails, 4 classes of railroads, various types of air fields, and 3 types of internal boundaries. Coverage complete in 20 sheets. Set includes various editions and issues of some sheets. Military grid. Index to place names on these maps is issued by U.S. Board on Geographical Names under title: Gazetteer to maps of Java, Madura and Bali. "Glossary" included on 2d- edition. Includes index to adjoining sheets.
